dc_title_s: Land Use and Landcover: Russian River Tributaries, Mendcino County, California, 1992
dc_description_s: This line shapefile represents existing riparian vegetation, land use and landcover of the Russian River and tributaries in its Mendocino Reach.This layer can be used for land use analysis and planning in the Russian River region of California.
